<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTA16">
<l>cīrāṟ piṟantu ciṟappāl vaḷarātu</l>
<l>pērvāma ṉākākkāṟ pērāḷā mārpārap</l>
<l>pulkinī yuṇṭumiḻnta pūminī rēṟparitē</l>
<l>collunī yāmaṟiyac cūḻntu.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Having been born from excellence, not growing out of superiority</l>
<l>at the time when [your] name was not [yet] Vāmāṉ, o great man, was it difficult</l>
<l>to accept water for the earth that you had embraced, for [your] chest to be full,</l>
<l>eaten [and] spat out? Speak, you, for us to know encompassingly.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
